{"tid":500884,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"不如唔好叫Facebook, 叫Adbook算啦","createTime":"2017-12-16T09:03:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-16T09:25:30.000Z","uid":17245,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"4b48573e5517a7a7fbae4c6482e0ad7ac92e6d34","tid":500884,"uid":17245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T09:03:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://chinese.engadget.com/2017/12/15/facebook-to-test-ads-in-front-of-watch-videos/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchinese.engadget.com%2F2017%2F12%2F15%2Ffacebook-to-test-ads-in-front-of-watch-videos%2F&d=S4kTmJZgfEkq1OG%2Fkmv%2FJghMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=53b387ac\" target=\"_blank\">https://chinese.engadget.com/2017/12/15/facebook-to-test-ads-in-front-of-watch-videos/</a><br />\n<br />\nFacebook 已經施行在影片中途加插廣告的做法，但他們似乎並沒有滿足，想要在影片開始之前就先來一小段廣告，不過幸好的是據說這新加入的廣告時段沒有過往的煩人。Facebook 計劃了明年在已經於海外開通的 Watch 欄位的影片裡插播 6 秒的廣告，所以這廣告並不會影響到動態時報上的影片，就只有在使用者真正準備好去看影片之時才會出現。<br />\n緊隨的自然就是在動態時報上的排序改變了，Facebook 正更新系統來讓受喜歡，或是時下流行的影片更容易被找到（像是在搜尋工具或專頁）。<br />\n<br />\n兩個改變的目標都很明顯，是 Facebook 想要透過插播廣告，以及影片的觸及率（觀看數）來增加影片部分的收入，讓影片製作者有著更大的誘因去拍攝影片。所以 Facebook 現在就希望在測試裡找到平衡點，在最大限度地加入廣告的情況下，保持使用者的持續觀看。"},{"pid":"b8a8d27f442cdcc3903a38d01bf8f7b7dbd1ff39","tid":500884,"uid":59278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T09:11:19.000Z","msg":"你facebook follow緊嘅page咪又係廣告<br />\n仲有人真係當佢「社交平台」㗎咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nSor for又中又英<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec37772c2d805d78d8de1957f02c706253685fba","tid":500884,"uid":17245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T09:19:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你facebook follow緊嘅page咪又係廣告<br />\n仲有人真係當佢「社交平台」㗎咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nSor for又中又英<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nFacebook ac 已 delete"},{"pid":"d2336ffb81f917095a5bc33c781ffa73f2ed39d4","tid":500884,"uid":150618,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T09:25:30.000Z","msg":"不如唔好叫lihkg，叫adhkg啦屌"}]}